Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.50,0:00:10.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,餵雛 你看看這屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一直保持著原樣直到你出院啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:17.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就打掃一下屋子 可怎麼就變成了這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.57,0:00:21.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說啊 說啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.24,0:00:24.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連我剛買的壺都陣亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.90,0:00:26.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會再原諒你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.61,0:00:29.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你斷絕關係
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,,0,0,0,,OP
