Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:44.40,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}偶然一瞬 想起了你的容貌模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:01:05.48,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}在記憶之中 你微笑著的側臉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:11.16,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}平淡無奇的日常 是無可替的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.24,0:01:16.01,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}這份思念之情 現在終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:18.82,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你歡笑度過的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.63,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}和你爭論淚流的曾經
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:25.99,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們攜手的每一天 令人無比憐愛的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:28.76,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}十分珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:34.19,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我們究竟相距多遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.54,0:01:40.44,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}我又回憶起你的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.52,0:01:45.25,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}遙遙可見的那條街道的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.34,0:01:49.74,hinamatsuri_opcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\blur6}你正展露著笑容嗎
