Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:07.35,hinamatsuri_guochang,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(960,0)\pos(614,1218)}斷絕關係Rock n' Roll Fever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:08.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你再像之前一樣恐嚇威脅我也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正這裡都亂成一團了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.09,0:02:17.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 儘管保你的重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.00,0:02:24.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:25.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:37.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以後要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:42.87,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,反正他也給我錢了 先去吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:52.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢了 以後要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.28,0:02:54.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,先打打遊戲再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:02:57.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是雛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:00.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你還沒有回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.47,0:03:05.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一言難盡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:08.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 你也搞砸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:10.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好好道過歉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.03,0:03:13.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,歉是道了 但他沒原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 這麼一點不夠吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.49,0:03:16.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你以後打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:26.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回新田那兒去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:29.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:34.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總之你就先在我這兒住下吧 你自己快想點辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:44.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:49.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼啊 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:11.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:19.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔給你 這是今天的雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:21.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 杏子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給你錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.15,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:26.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去撿空罐子了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:33.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 差不多該醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:36.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自吃別人的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:39.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你想過以後的計劃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了 不過不知道該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:45.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,遊戲機都沒電了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙 到底想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:49.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,芳香醇厚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:51.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛不在家 白天也能品嘗美酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:57.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說這傻丫頭哭著回來求我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:04.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是渡邊中學的三島
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.94,0:05:06.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是那個調酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.84,0:05:08.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我是雛的同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我給她拿來了學校的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:12.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:14.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能放在信箱裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.48,0:05:19.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 雛感冒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:23.12,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在有點不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.61,0:05:25.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她回我老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.10,0:05:29.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還有學校這檔子事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是假期 為什麼會回老家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這又是家事 不好過問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:41.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,詩子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在人手不夠了 過來幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.14,0:05:48.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幫什麼忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.27,0:05:54.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,可以再給我一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 還要給別人呢 平等平等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:05:59.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:00.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:02.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 詩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:06.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼會在這兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:07.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,給我飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 快一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.36,0:06:12.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.94,0:06:16.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛 咱們該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小瞳吧 真是幫了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:22.95,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.09,0:06:24.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道小雛最近出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:31.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,斷絕關係
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.32,0:06:34.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這麼狠心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是沒看到那個慘相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底 你知道那傢伙費了我多少錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是一點好處都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:50.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,養孩子怎麼能說什麼好處不好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是看她孤身一人才收留她的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.47,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我確實是這麼說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:01.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是這小屁孩的老爸 不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:09.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能跟他們說雛是突然從天上掉下來的就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你啊 我一直沒插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你這口氣算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:15.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣你還算是個父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:19.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不論如何這樣還是太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是無話可說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:32.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你們究竟是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.29,0:07:38.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,滾出去……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 去拿鹽過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:55.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:56.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.42,0:07:58.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你得把新田的酒錢付了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:05.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不管她現在過得怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連杏子都努力活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.23,0:08:12.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定行的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我還特意坐了單人沙發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.88,0:08:23.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,落了個壞習慣啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,蠟燭可不是免費的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.10,0:08:34.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我再看一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:37.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那本雜誌本來是能賣錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:38.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我很閒嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:41.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,薯片吃完了 沒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.10,0:08:46.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便吃我的東西 懶懶散散就會在這睡懶覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就沒考慮過要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:54.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我不照顧你了 我要和你絕交
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,以後該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:06.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,跟新田在一起的時候真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.37,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但我怎麼才能回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,他最生氣的就是我把壺弄碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錢
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——插入曲——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.40,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}眩しいすぎるぜ　サンライズ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}でもまだ僕でいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}遠すぎる二人のたり
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:37.94,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}それはディスタンス
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:28.40,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}過於耀眼的Sunrise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}但是仍想保持自我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:32.50,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}分隔得過於遙遠的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:37.94,hinamatsuri_insert,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}這就是Distance
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——插入曲——
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:51.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚真是幹得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:54.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,淳你這歌喉還是一如既往的棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.56,0:10:00.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:02.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才就在這裡聽了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.73,0:10:05.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們樂隊怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:08.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個先不提 我想問你們一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.06,0:10:14.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,分發食物的時候她們還在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.28,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那她應該去杏子那邊住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒並不是在意她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:25.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是來看看她 確認一下她是不是因為我死翹翹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.31,0:10:26.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:27.21,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是杏子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹什麼在這裡鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:31.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒 沒什麼 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,散步啦 散步
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:36.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,散步就在公園門口轉來轉去嗎 是不是腦子出問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.17,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不說這個了 先說說雛的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:42.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,連你也要責怪我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.06,0:10:43.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:49.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前真能把她照顧好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我三天就跟她絕交了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:55.79,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙 連流浪漢都不如
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:06.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,杏子 就算你現在展示你的活法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:14.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒耍小聰明 也沒有機關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.87,0:11:24.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,小雛 你這魔術好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:28.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們雖然原來在這兒是最賣座的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.33,0:11:29.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但最近被你給打敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等下咱們去吃個飯慶祝一下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:33.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.20,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 我找到小雛了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:42.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊來找我哭一哭 認個錯就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:45.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛這傢伙弄得我這麼不安
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,——插入曲——
