Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:16.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝大家 雖然正High著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:18.78,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是今天最後一曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:21.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起來 我也一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.02,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,Angel！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.58,0:12:26.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,Angel！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:31.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.50,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你這兒聚這麼多人 得交申請才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.99,0:12:36.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 解散解散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.18,0:12:39.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:40.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你明天也要來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:53.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:56.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真得超嗨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.89,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這下子離正式出道也不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了小雛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:03.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,大家對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.01,0:13:12.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我要退出樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.57,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們一起以武道館為目標吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:17.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,算了吧淳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你好好看看小雛的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:25.91,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼重要的事物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:33.63,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就讓我們為小雛踏上新生活而獻上祝願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:35.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說啊 是她自己有事做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還擔心她我是真的傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:47.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在你們正式和好之前禁止來這喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.18,0:14:00.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這不是擔心得很嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:11.67,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:17.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼事 我應該說了跟你斷絕關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:20.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 反正不在我身邊你也有事可做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:29.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是和新田在一起的時光是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.30,0:14:34.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:35.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:38.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:43.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個壺是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:45.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我打碎壺之後 新田你生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:47.22,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是把這個作為賠禮的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.46,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,看著就很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:50.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,花了多少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:52.62,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,2900日元
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.72,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不知道打碎的壺是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:56.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就買了這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.16,0:15:02.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,新田
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:07.16,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,還愣著做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.54,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:23.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.90,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 關門的時候輕一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.73,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近很多店鋪都拒絕接待黑幫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:45.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 世道真的是越來越艱難了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:47.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.48,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:53.24,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天才第一次光顧的店裡一不小心就發起了牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就跟新田說的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:58.32,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這是因為美酒而導致嘴巴都變鬆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:15:59.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這不也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.95,0:16:03.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在那扇門外有不變的生活在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.99,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在這裡有片刻能做坦率的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.74,0:16:12.39,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我想酒吧 一定是擁有這樣的氛圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.29,0:16:17.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 就讓我再來叨擾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:23.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,最近啊 不得不謹慎對待和學生們的關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:26.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,家長們和教育委員會也很煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:30.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看您焦頭爛額的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:34.30,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我想一定也有正將老師您的努力看在眼裡的學生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:39.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳… 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.06,0:16:52.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也是為了讓客人們開心才調酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何時開始就做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.21,0:17:01.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,變成了想著「不能睡著就盆滿缽盈嗎」的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然說只是週末
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.37,0:17:18.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是工作到天亮果然還是太勉強了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.72,0:17:21.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在朋友家過夜這個謊言也差不多不能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.95,0:17:24.11,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,要怎麼跟詩子小姐說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.06,0:17:30.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是之前大清早就在撿易拉罐的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:37.00,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:40.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫瞳 在那邊的店裡工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.86,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫杏子 在撿易拉罐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:49.13,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 你應該不是志願者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:50.60,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,撿來的易拉罐我拿去換錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.14,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這是在哪個國家？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的話 再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.04,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.25,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛 我也是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.82,0:18:04.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你能跟我來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:09.09,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 泰叔說不能跟不認識的人走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.27,0:18:10.36,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.38,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是說撿易拉罐就沒關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.69,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道一個有很多易拉罐的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.65,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:22.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿部先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,噢小瞳 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:28.05,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿部先生你店裡易拉罐有挺多的對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.96,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 這個時間點垃圾要扔出來嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.27,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,能把易拉罐給她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.54,0:18:42.74,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個女孩子一直都在這附近撿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.74,0:18:45.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過啊 擅自做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:48.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,您家店長經常在我這邊喝酒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:52.85,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,阿部先生這個時間段會翹班 我在幫你保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:55.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這可頭疼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.40,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,真敵不過小瞳你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.61,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我在的時候 你隨時可以過來拿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:04.81,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我翹班的事能幫我保密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:07.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 瞬間就收滿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.38,0:19:09.56,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,你真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 我沒做什麼大不了的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.08,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢 你好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:15.75,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.31,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔說了 受恩必當回報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說泰叔到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:29.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已經想回去睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.67,0:19:32.26,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 跟上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好不安啊 她父母是怎樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.10,0:19:39.10,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,應該很窮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.33,0:19:41.98,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:43.70,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,公園？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:47.88,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.03,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,貧窮遠超出我想像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:54.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 杏子 那孩子是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 泰叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.76,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,泰叔是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:59.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,她是瞳 我請她來家裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.06,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是流浪漢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:03.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:05.77,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.07,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且應了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.33,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 這是第一次交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:18.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,原來瞳你是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.76,0:20:21.66,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.64,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得好沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.18,0:20:27.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,來吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.71,0:20:29.71,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是回禮所以請你吃比平時更豪華的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個整整要200日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:34.92,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:39.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你能賺多少錢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:42.51,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話賣賣易拉罐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:44.42,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,一天能賺600日元左右呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.16,0:20:48.29,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我連半小時都不用就能賺到這個數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.98,0:20:51.53,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.80,0:20:52.68,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:55.80,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我之前還賣到過750日元哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:56.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:57.97,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是我的最高紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.41,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.55,0:21:04.44,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,拉麵 吃不下去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:07.55,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不過今天很簡單就能收工了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:09.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不用走一整天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:15.19,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下來就有空了 也能玩玩放鬆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.18,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.49,0:21:17.93,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,那現在去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.83,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,現在？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:30.84,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去你會一直都是鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.52,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,這個捉鬼要玩到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.68,0:21:38.82,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說 為什麼是捉鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.21,0:21:40.94,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.34,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:49.01,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,已經 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.45,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.26,0:21:54.23,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,瞳？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.59,hinamatsuri_text,NTP,0,0,0,,站著睡著了！
